<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The function uses the macro _MHD_static_inline which expands to a compiler-specific attribute (__attribute__((always_inline))). The use of __attribute__((...)) is a GCC/clang language extension; thus the declaration of digest_reset employs a compiler extension and violates MISRA C 2023 Rule 1.2.
</scenario>
